Patrick Thomas (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_Thomas_(actor) 0 Patrick Thomas (born February 21, 1961) is an American actor and voice actor. Thomas has had roles in several different TV shows and movies. He has also done voice acting. He also goes by the aliases Pat Thomas, Puppy Thomas, and Courtney Burr.
